"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-eiffel-tower-international-olympic-committee-netherlands-paris-nbc-b2587020.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Dark clouds continued to gather over the Olympic beach volleyball venue in the shadow of theEiffel Toweron Saturday, but it was not only the unrelenting drizzle that was a cause for concern.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The sport has revelled in its role as a care-free and often sun-kissed pursuit since its inaugural appearance on the Olympic programme in 1996, its profile bolstered by high-profile locations from Horse Guard's Parade to the golden sands of Copacabana.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris2024 organisers were clearly intent on continuing the tradition when they placed the sport squarely beneath the city's most famous landmark, a choice not lost on arguably its most illustrious competitor, three-time champion Misty May-Treanor.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Misty_May-Treanor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Misty May-Treanor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Misty_May-Treanor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Misty_May-Treanor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American, who won three consecutive gold medals from 2004 to 2012, and is back in Paris as a commentary for theNBCnetwork, said: \\\"I got lucky because my last Games were at Horse Guard's Parade.\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1045, \"end\": 1053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999993438661402, \"rank\": 4.877516919492069e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998708518, \"rank\": 1.2920822993846938e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was quite the venue but this one, the night matches are going to be spectacular.\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are trying to up (the level at each Games).\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know whatAustraliaare going to do (for Brisbane 2032).\\\"\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Beach volleyball's popularity was evident in the sizeable crowd that still showed up for the opening day of preliminary matches on Saturday, despite the Trocadero stadium being open to the elements.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it is not just the weather that is causing the sport's carefully cultivated, happy-go-lucky image to take a battering in the French capital.\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1771, \"end\": 1777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9947983168742534, \"rank\": 0.005140782250693703, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The inclusion of Steven Van de Velde, a 29-year-old Dutch player who was convicted of raping a 12-year-old British girl in 2016, has caused questions to be asked over whether theInternational Olympic Committeeshould have intervened.\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 2020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.8665945230904455, \"rank\": 0.14502703790061441, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1895, \"end\": 1902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9981266117690653, \"rank\": 0.001207715012366394, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde is understood not to be staying in the Olympic Village at his own request, and will be allowed to forego the usual post-match mixed zone interviews.\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2074, \"end\": 2089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.6420812446432638e-13, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dutch Olympic Committee maintains Van de Velde has been successfully rehabilitated and deserves his place in the squad.\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2188, \"end\": 2211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 6.8199576222256784e-12, \"text\": \"Dutch Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite mounting criticism of Van de Velde's involvement, the International Olympic Committee indicated that it has no plans to bar him from competing, although its spokesman Mark Adams implied a degree of discomfort in reaching the decision.\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2371, \"end\": 2402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2484, \"end\": 2494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"score\": 0.5137413298825356, \"rank\": 0.45833333333342063, \"text\": \"Mark Adams\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(London 2012) was quite the venue but this one, the night matches are going to be spectacular.\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are trying to up (the level at each Games)  Asked if the IOC was \\\"comfortable and happy\\\" with Van de Velde's involvement, its spokesman Mark Adams said: \\\"I think to characterise it as \\\"comfortable and happy\\\" would not be correct.\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2710, \"end\": 2713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2239078696938586e-23, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2789, \"end\": 2799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"score\": 0.5137413298825356, \"rank\": 0.45833333333342063, \"text\": \"Mark Adams\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think a crime occurred some time ago, 10 years ago.\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2938, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A great deal of rehabilitation has taken place, and there is very strong safeguarding in place also, and I believe\\u2026 the athlete in question is not even staying in the village.\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 3114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So we feel that the Dutch National Olympic committee have explained their decision.\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3137, \"end\": 3169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dutch National Olympic committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Comfortable, happy, you can characterise it how you want but we feel that the statement that they have given us is correct and we will continue with the situation as it is.\\\"\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3512, \"entities\": []}]}"